name: Urgent Quest
desc: The Order Description is limited to X characters.
editor_name: 测试订单-紧急

name: Tailored Order
desc: The Order Description is limited to X characters.
editor_name: 测试订单-定制

name: Random Order 1
desc: The Order Description is limited to X characters.
editor_name: 测试订单-随机1

name: Random Order 2
desc: The Order Description is limited to X characters.
editor_name: 测试订单-随机2

name: Specialty Promotion
desc: Exchange the local town's rye beer for essential medicines from Waverun City, and maybe some sea fish too.
editor_name: 浪涌城-特产换药R1

name: Supply Assurance
desc: Deliver food supplies to Windyvale Town to reassure its residents of sufficient food stocks and to thwart the plans of grain speculators.
editor_name: 周边小镇-稳定粮价R1

name: Provoke the Enemy
desc: It seems that as we continue our good deeds, bad buys will seek us out. Let's keep up the food deliveries, and meet those grain speculators.
editor_name: 周边小镇-稳定粮价R2

name: Mastermind
desc: With this batch of food delivered, the food crisis will be largely resolved, sending the speculators into a frenzy. Following our previous success in thwarting a dangerous attack, what awaits us next?
editor_name: 周边小镇-稳定粮价R3

name: Local Protection
desc: Our caravan encountered a deliberate obstacle in Waverun City. Those responsible must face consequences, or the entire city will never taste another sip of Convallaria's Rye Beer.
editor_name: 浪涌城-恶意竞争R1

name: Co-op Invitation
desc: In response to conflicts with the local Trading Post, we've decided to resolve them through collaboration. For this trade, we're bringing a cooperative proposal to the merchants of Waverun City.
editor_name: 浪涌城-恶意竞争R2

name: Large-Scale Construction
desc: The refugees have settled in Mine Pit, and we are planning to transport some construction stones there to help them build new homes.
editor_name: 矿坑城-建立矿坑城R1

name: Homeland Defense
desc: We are to deliver weapons to the Mine Pit citizens so they can defend themselves against the harassment of the Darklight.
editor_name: 矿坑城-建立矿坑城R2

name: Seeds of Hope
desc: The Mine Pit citizens can now defend themselves, but they still need some food and seeds to endure the final hardship and pursue long-term development.
editor_name: 矿坑城-建立矿坑城R3

name: Market Expansion
desc: We've found a golden trade opportunity from the contact details left by Acambe. If we deliver some mysterious goods to the Rabi'a Oasis, we'll receive a rich reward.
editor_name: 拉比亚绿洲-开拓市场R1

name: Golden Words
desc: We have got the herbs required by a certain 'know-it-all.' Our next move is to return to Rabi'a Oasis, in hopes that he will give us news about Acambe.
editor_name: 周边小镇-开拓市场R2

name: Dangerous Scent
desc: The air in Windyvale Town is tinged with the smell of gunpowder. This trade might just provide us with the answer.
editor_name: 周边小镇-重型武器出现R1

name: Follow the Scent
desc: It's strange that the people of Windyvale Town should be making powerful weapons. Perhaps this trade will bring us closer to the truth.
editor_name: 周边小镇-重型武器出现R2

name: Production Recovery
desc: With Mine Pit now firmly established and growing, we, as both their ally and investor, have decided to continue supporting its development.
editor_name: 矿坑城-恢复晶石生产R1

name: Luxite Rush
desc: Investing in Mine Pit proved wise as new Luxite veins were discovered deep in the mines. Now, we just need to send the right supplies to help them clear the troubles in the mines.
editor_name: 矿坑城-恢复晶石生产R2-A

name: Luxite Rush
desc: Investing in Mine Pit proved wise as new Luxite veins were discovered deep in the mines. Now, we just need to send the right supplies to help them clear the troubles in the mines.
editor_name: 矿坑城-恢复晶石生产R2-B

name: History Lover
desc: Tranquillo wants one of our ancient books. The history recorded in it appears irrelevant to our current business, so there should be no harm in giving it to him… right?
editor_name: 黑暗之光-和特兰奎洛的交易R1

name: Venture into Luxite Trading
desc: We've set out for Waverun City with the first batch of Luxites, and their tinkling in the crates sounds delightful.
editor_name: 浪涌城-二王子晶石生意R1

name: Familiar Route
desc: Following our highly successful Luxite trade with Lutfi, we're heading to Waverun City with even more Luxites this time.
editor_name: 浪涌城-二王子晶石生意R2

name: Negotiation First
desc: An unexpected rival Luxite supplier has emerged in Waverun City, causing the price to drop. We need to make contact with them to prevent unnecessary price wars.
editor_name: 浪涌城-二王子晶石生意R3

name: Journey to the Capital
desc: According to Inanna's suggestion, we should head to Mornrays Castle and demonstrate our reliable stance in this war through trade.
editor_name: 晨曦堡-前往晨曦堡R1

name: Barter
desc: Rumor has it that the nobles of Lightgloam City, obsessed with their longevity, drink a bizarre potion made from desert snakes every day.
editor_name: 暮光城-贿赂法皇国R1

name: Arms Supply
desc: The Vlderians need more weapons to defend themselves against the Elamanians.
editor_name: 薇尔德-薇尔德工艺品R1

name: Breaking Free
desc: With sufficient food supplies, the people of Windyvale Town will no longer be forced to produce dangerous explosives for sustenance.
editor_name: 周边小镇-援建周边小镇R1

name: Upgrade the Walls
desc: Given the critical security situation in Windyvale Town, we need to work with craftsmen from Mine Pit to help build robust walls.
editor_name: 周边小镇-援建周边小镇R2

name: A New Path
desc: We believe that this trade will mark a turning point for Windyvale Town, helping it shed the exploitation by others and regain its independence.
editor_name: 周边小镇-援建周边小镇R3

name: Herb Smuggling
desc: We need to risk smuggling Iria's local herbs through Rabi'a Oasis into Elaman, offering relief to the deeply afflicted slaves.
editor_name: 鹦鹉人的走私R1~RN

name: Patriotic Merchant
desc: Help Kadar transport his merchandise to Mornrays Castle.
editor_name: 晨曦堡-护送前往晨曦堡R1

name: Into the Dark
desc: As Mine Pit flourishes, the Darklight's dominance wanes. It's time to help the awakened souls escape the darkness.
editor_name: 黑暗之光-帮助黑光改邪归正R1

name: Arms Order - Mornrays Castle
desc: Knowing that this will temporarily escalate the war in Iria, you still decide to send arms to Mornrays Castle, for… a long-term goal?
editor_name: 晨曦堡-军火订单R1

name: Arms Order - Waverun City
desc: Knowing that this will temporarily escalate the war in Iria, you still decide to send arms to Waverun City, for… a long-term goal?
editor_name: 浪涌城-军火订单R1

name: Upgrade Houses
desc: Believing in the Vlder's integral role in peace, we decide to help build their tribe.
editor_name: 薇尔德-援建薇尔德R1

name: Road Expansion
desc: We decide to help Vlder widen their roads that connect to Iria's primary commercial routes.
editor_name: 薇尔德-援建薇尔德R2

name: Tranquillo Trade
desc: The Papal States want Tranquillo, and we happen to have him.
editor_name: 暮光城-交易特兰奎洛R1

name: History Lover II
desc: Taair wants an ancient book; let's hope it's still in our storage.
editor_name: 周边小镇-塔埃尔的收藏R1

name: Purchase Luxites - Mornrays Castle
desc: Procure a batch of Luxites from Mornrays Castle. They always have a steady supply, but at a high price.
editor_name: 晨曦堡-晶石贸易委托R1

name: Purchase Luxites - Lightgloam City
desc: Procure a batch of Luxites from Lightgloam City. Their price will drop only after the Papal States fully open up Luxite exports.
editor_name: 暮光城-晶石贸易委托R1

name: Sell Luxites - Oasis
desc: Sell a batch of Luxites to Rabi'a Oasis. The Elamanians have an insatiable desire for Luxites and are willing to offer the highest prices.
editor_name: 拉比亚绿洲-晶石贸易委托R1

name: Purchase Luxites - Mine Pit
desc: Procure a batch of Luxites from Mine Pit. As a partner of the "Fox and Squirrel" Luxite Mining Consortium, we can buy their Luxites at very low prices, albeit in limited quantities.
editor_name: 矿坑城-晶石贸易委托R1

name: Sell Luxites - First Batch
desc: Sell a batch of Luxites to Waverun City. The peace in Iria currently hinges on the amount and speed of the Luxites we sell to the Advance Order.
editor_name: 浪涌城-晶石贸易委托R1

name: Purchase Luxites - Vlder
desc: Procure a batch of Luxites from Vlder. As a partner of the "Fox and Squirrel" Luxite Mining Consortium, we can buy their Luxites at very low prices, albeit in very unstable quantities.
editor_name: 薇尔德-晶石贸易委托R1

name: Iggy's New Discovery
desc: We decide to sponsor a supply of resources for Iggy's treasure-hunting activities, hoping his explorations yield fruitful results.
editor_name: 薇尔德-晶石贸易委托R2

name: Further Support
desc: Despite Iggy's previous unsuccessful exploration, his unwavering confidence has persuaded us to give him another chance and provide more resources.
editor_name: 薇尔德-晶石贸易委托R3

name: Royalty Obsession
desc: Deliver regal artifacts to a noble in Lightgloam City on Garcia's behalf, with a futures contract as our reward.
editor_name: 暮光城-王权收集癖R1

name: Purchase Special Dyes
desc: We've finally figured out how to buy from the dye merchant at Rabi'a Oasis—we're in the know now! What a great trade opportunity!
editor_name: 拉比亚绿洲-买染料R1

name: Bribe Miguel
desc: Miguel's pricing may be off the charts, but the value matches the cost. He'll support us in important battles and share secrets about the Papal States. What a knack for the trade he has.
editor_name: 暮光城-收买米格尔R1

name: Secret Meeting with Lutfi
desc: We’re heading to Waverun City once again at Lutfi's invitation, and this time, he seems to have something special planned.
editor_name: 浪涌城-评议会手谕R1

name: Playing Messenger
desc: Deliver Lutfi's message to Prince Dantalion.
editor_name: 浪涌城-评议会手谕R2

name: Proof
desc: Deliver the token symbolizing the sincere bond between the two princes.
editor_name: 浪涌城-评议会手谕R3

name: New Order - Waverun City
desc: A new client from Waverun City has placed an order with us. By delivering their desired goods, we'll receive a fitting reward. Completing enough of these orders could make them a major client and secure larger future orders.
editor_name: 随机订单_浪涌城_栏位少_初始_奖励角色技能

name: [Recruit] A Fresh Start
desc: A deserter from the Elamanian Faceless hopes to make a fresh start through a trade. We can manage this deal en route to Lightgloam City.
editor_name: 招募事件订单-埃拉曼双刀兵

name: [Trial] Herb Shortage
desc: We've accepted a task from a medicine merchant to collect high-quality herbs on our way to Windyvale Town. However, we must stay alert for packs of wild wolves in the area.
editor_name: 考验关卡订单-P2

name: [Trial] Act in Collusion
desc: We've taken on a mercenary's quest for revenge: en route to Mornrays Castle, we are to keep an eye out for a group of Darklight Conjurers and Outlaws, and eliminate them completely.
editor_name: 考验关卡订单-P3

name: [Trial] Lonely Promise
desc: We’ve agreed to help the Vlderian Dancer look for someone. En route to Rabi'a Oasis, we’ll drop by the trading post where her friend works.
editor_name: 考验关卡订单-P4

name: [Trial] Dog-eat-dog
desc: We came across a Luxite Hunter ousted from his squad, who is now seeking revenge on his former mates by exposing their raid plan to us. Fully armed and prepared, we are on our way to Lightgloam City for battle.
editor_name: 考验关卡订单-P5-1

name: [Trial] Luxite Hunter
desc: We've taken on a quest from a Luxite Merchant to head to Rabi'a Oasis and retrieve goods stolen by Luxite Hunters, but the merchant seems to be holding back some details.
editor_name: 考验关卡订单-P5-2

name: Sell Dyes
desc: Having obtained Elaman's Premium Dyes, we can now sell them to the nobles at Mornrays Castle for a hefty profit, enough to buy out the continent's top mercenary group.
editor_name: 拉比亚绿洲-买染料R2

name: Sell Luxites - Second Batch
desc: Sell another batch of Luxites to Waverun City. The peace in Iria currently hinges on the amount and speed of the Luxites we sell to the Advance Order.
editor_name: 浪涌城-晶石贸易委托R2
